snippet.title: NET:Zone Intro
snippet.description:
NET:Zone
A game made back in 1996, developed by Compro Games and published by GameTek.
A cyberpunk click adventuregame. That i used allot of my time to beat :P
I will now play it again recording my way trough this weird cyberspacegame.
